Step 1) sudo apt install samba -y
Step 2) sudo nano /etc/samba/smb.conf
Step 3) ensure under Global Settings>[global] that workgroup = WORKGROUP
Step 4) at the end paste in:
[devicename]
    path = /home/username
    valid users = @username
    browsable = yes
    writeable = yes
    read only = no
Step 5) ctrl+s and ctrl+x
Step 6) sudo smbpasswd -a ubuntuusername
Step 7) enter password
Step 8) Map Network Drive on Windows PC
